    /* Hades Fountain / StoryReset Screen */
    {
      Id = "StoryResetIntro"
      DisplayName = "Myths Retold"
      Description = """
      Thank you for playing {#AlertHeaderFormat}Hades II{#Prev}, and congratulations on your victory!

      Here, you may choose to {#AlertItalicFormat}turn back Time {#Prev}to an earlier possible point in the story, in which {#AlertHighlightFormat}Melinoë {#Prev}has fought, but not yet vanquished, {#AlertHighlightFormat}Chronos {#Prev}and {#AlertHighlightFormat}Typhon{#Prev}... thus shall her tale be retold!

     · This lets you {#AlertBoldFormat}re-experience key events in the story{#Prev}, or experience rare events you may have missed, without resetting the rest of your progress.

     · Most of {#AlertBoldFormat}your progress will be preserved{#Prev}. Any {#AlertBoldFormat}{!Icons.MixerIBoss} Z·Sand {#Prev}and {#AlertBoldFormat}{!Icons.MixerQBoss} V·Lens {#Prev}you have will be restored after the end credits. Just about everything else you have already unlocked will remain unlocked.

     · If you have not yet fulfilled the Fated List Prophecy {#AlertBoldFormat}Melinoë, Help Us{#Prev}, bear in mind it can only be fulfilled after the end credits.

    {#AlertItalicFormat}Note: {#Prev}Only key events in the story will be reset if you proceed.
    """
    }
    {
