    {
      Id = "ShrineIntro"
      DisplayName = "The Oath"
      Description = """
      {#AlertItalicFormat}Salutations! {#Prev}You are worthy of the {#AlertHeaderFormat}Oath of the Unseen{#Prev}, and may now enact the {#AlertHighlightFormat}{$Keywords.Bounties} of Night{#Prev}, if you dare. Thus it is done:

      · Activate various {#AlertHighlightFormat}Vows {#Prev}to raise {!Icons.ShrinePoint}{#AlertBoldFormat}Fear{#Prev}, a measure of adversity.

      · Then, pursue the marked {#BoldFormat}{$Keywords.Boss} {#Prev}using the specified weapon.

      · Prevail, and earn {!Icons.WeaponPointsRare}{#AlertBoldFormat}Nightmare {#Prev}for upgrades in the {#AlertBoldFormat}Silver Pool{#Prev}.

      Many {#AlertHighlightFormat}Vows {#Prev}can be intensified to raise {!Icons.ShrinePoint}{#AlertBoldFormat}Fear {#Prev}even more, though you are also free to rescind {#AlertHighlightFormat}Vows {#Prev}without consequence. Your continued service to the realm is appreciated either way.

      {!Icons.DivLong}

      {#AlertItalicFormat}Hint: {#Prev}Enact available {#AlertHighlightFormat}{$Keywords.Bounties} {#Prev}to reveal more. If one proves to be a struggle, you may switch weapons to attempt another!
    """
    }
